# MenRush logo — single source of truth

The MenRush logo is the **bronze two-profile medallion** with "MENRUSH" at the bottom. It is **not** a CSS animation, radar icon, wordmark-only treatment, or AI-generated variant.

## Canonical asset

- **Master file (never delete or swap):** `frontend/public/brand/menrush-logo.png`
- **UI display sizes:** generated from master — `medallion-480.png`, `medallion-380.png`
- **Favicons / PWA:** `frontend/public/brand/icon-*.png` (generated from master)
- **Emails:** `frontend/public/menrush-logo.png` and `email-assets/menrush-logo.png` (copies of master)

## Code

- All public pages use `BrandMark` → `BRAND_MEDALLION` from `frontend/src/lib/brand.ts`
- **Do not** remove `BrandMark` from `/`, `/coming-soon`, `/beta`, `/login`, `/register`, or in-app chrome
- **Do not** replace the medallion with CSS shapes, CoinFlip, radar animations, or text-only wordmarks
- **Do not** add new logo PNGs with different artwork — only resize the master

## Regenerating sizes

If the master is updated, run from `frontend/`:

```bash
node scripts/sync-brand-logo.mjs
```

Never hand-edit or AI-generate derivative PNGs.

## Forbidden

- Removing the logo from public/auth pages
- Introducing `CoinFlip`, `mr-radar_*` animations, or alternate logo components
- Pointing UI at `logo.png`, `images/logo.jpeg`, or unrelated assets
